{"tid":2079182,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁愛詩：如国安認為有需要截聽、搜屋、甚至直接拉人，「唔係唔做得」","createTime":"2020-06-25T15:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T03:24:35.000Z","uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"1be4bbaa873fa4bb8aa813310ca9c0c584a584ce","tid":2079182,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:21:02.000Z","msg":"國安法下，內地將會在港成立維護國家安全公署，梁指，公署在執行任務時要守香港法律，調查時如需要截聽或搜屋，也要向法庭申請批准，與香港警察沒有分別。<span style=\"color: red;\">至於公署能否拉人？梁愛詩指可以</span>，但這視乎警方與公署的協調，「唔係做唔到」，舉例指如公署偵察後，會與警務處國家安全的部門協調，由警方拘捕，但如果案件極度機密，公署可以保留有關拘捕權力：「佢要馬上行事，都要有權做，但要跟香港法律。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200625/XOA3LQ3PBOWSIKNB4APCK4COXE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200625%2FXOA3LQ3PBOWSIKNB4APCK4COXE%2F&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=303aa6e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200625%2FXOA3LQ3PBOWSIKNB4APCK4COXE%2F&h=2837d6a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200625/XOA3LQ3PBOWSIKNB4APCK4COXE/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85da68df54dec8e77dca342c5e366d6ee9d44479","tid":2079182,"uid":41545,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:21:55.000Z","msg":"咁點夠辣 緊係要加埋打靶啦"},{"pid":"aabef8840385e1a434a579558e14b2bf010150cd","tid":2079182,"uid":263648,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"1be4bbaa873fa4bb8aa813310ca9c0c584a584ce","tid":2079182,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:21:02.000Z","msg":"國安法下，內地將會在港成立維護國家安全公署，梁指，公署在執行任務時要守香港法律，調查時如需要截聽或搜屋，也要向法庭申請批准，與香港警察沒有分別。<span style=\"color: red;\">至於公署能否拉人？梁愛詩指可以</span>，但這視乎警方與公署的協調，「唔係做唔到」，舉例指如公署偵察後，會與警務處國家安全的部門協調，由警方拘捕，但如果案件極度機密，公署可以保留有關拘捕權力：「佢要馬上行事，都要有權做，但要跟香港法律。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200625/XOA3LQ3PBOWSIKNB4APCK4COXE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200625%2FXOA3LQ3PBOWSIKNB4APCK4COXE%2F&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=303aa6e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200625%2FXOA3LQ3PBOWSIKNB4APCK4COXE%2F&h=2837d6a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200625/XOA3LQ3PBOWSIKNB4APCK4COXE/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:22:30.000Z","msg":"正，唔好話外資，港資、中資民企個個走。"},{"pid":"7fd8d16f6028c47c1e077e5eb7a48a1a0bd91aaa","tid":2079182,"uid":132587,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:28:01.000Z","msg":"中共做野永遠都偷偷摸摸<br />\n宜家仲唔公開條文內容<br />\n係咁搵人出黎試水溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一公佈條文一定激發香港上年612果種決心<br />\n宜家我地靜左只係因為未殺到<br />\n心諗國安法姐 同告暴動咪差唔多<br />\n<br />\n根本全世界同香港就係得緊佢公開條文呢一刻<br />\n國際同香港就會黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd93ae6b8d41fe1099a9dbd493cc1e0a7ceeda95","tid":2079182,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />."},{"pid":"f198884dce482f48157a1fb57f622cca6de82fe5","tid":2079182,"uid":60977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:30:23.000Z","msg":"快撚啲立法<br />\n設埋機構<br />\n肅清曬"},{"pid":"2f3e00e0e705b1a66f98501666eccbb0f7629e8d","tid":2079182,"uid":153239,"like":